Dr. Pollack's Background






Bio


Kenneth L. Pollack, MD practices Pain Medicine in West Des Moines, IA. Dr. Pollack graduated from University of Illinois College of Medicine in 1985 and has been in practice for 32 years. He completed a residency at University of Iowa Hospitals & Clinics. He currently practices at Des Moines Orthopaedic Surgeons PC and is affiliated with Blank Children's Hospital, Boone County Hospital and Broadlawns Medical Center. Dr. Pollack accepts multiple insurance plans including Aetna, Wellmark and Medicare. Dr. Pollack is board certified in Anesthesiology. In addition to English, Dr. Pollack's practice supports this language: Spanish. 





