Bio









                                        Dr.
                                        Pollack                                        has

                                        
                                            one office                                        
                                        in
                                        Iowa                                                                                    where he                                                                                                                            specializes in
                                            Interventional Pain Management.                                                                            

                                                                                    Dr. Pollack works with twenty-nine doctors                                            including Dr. Megan Brady                                             and Dr. Patricia Kallemeier.
                                                                                
















             Specialty        







 


Interventional Pain Management 

                                As an interventional pain management specialist in Iowa, Dr. Pollack focuses on relieving chronic pain in patients. Interventional pain specialists offer pain relief by blocking or interrupting the transmission of neurological pain signals in the brain. Dr. Pollack may perform treatments such as spinal cord and nerve stimulation, nerve or medial branch blocks, medication management, or the implantation of drug delivery systems.                            






 


            Languages Spoken  
                    




